events.title: the 2nd Earl of Essex is executed

movie.title: Anonymous
movie.plot: Edward De Vere, Earl of Oxford, is presented as the real author of Shakespeare's works. Edward's life is followed through flashbacks from a young child, through to the end of his life. He is portrayed as a child prodigy who writes and performs A Midsummer Night's Dream for a young Elizabeth I. A series of events sees his plays being performed by a frontman, Shakespeare.
movie.awards: Nominated for 1 Oscar. Another 7 wins & 11 nominations.

events.title: Muhammad Ali beats Sonny Liston to become heavyweight champion of the world

movie.title: King of the World
movie.plot: The early career of boxer Muhammad Ali, then known as Cassius Clay, as he prepares for a title fight against Sonny Liston, while struggling to come to terms with his private and public personas.
